Kind: captions

00:00:08.408 --> 00:00:11.178 position:27% line:89% align:start
[whimsical music]

00:00:15.182 --> 00:00:18.018 position:27% line:89% align:start
[birds chirping]

00:00:43.210 --> 00:00:47.114 position:10% line:89% align:start
[lighthearted acoustic music]

00:01:23.651 --> 00:01:26.621 position:27% line:89% align:start
[music continues]

00:01:42.336 --> 00:01:45.607 position:30% line:89% align:start
[wind blowing]

00:02:15.603 --> 00:02:18.673 position:19% line:89% align:start
[Yui breathes heavily]

00:02:27.782 --> 00:02:30.885 position:30% line:83% align:start
Cape Fox Cub is
what they call this place.

00:02:30.918 --> 00:02:33.821 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Yui panting]

00:02:34.956 --> 00:02:36.490 position:24% line:89% align:start
Just a bit further.

00:02:39.661 --> 00:02:42.229 position:27% line:89% align:start
[birds chirping]

00:03:48.863 --> 00:03:49.997 position:33% line:89% align:start
Here we are.

00:03:50.031 --> 00:03:52.432 position:7% line:89% align:start
Welcome to our new home, girls.

00:03:52.466 --> 00:03:53.366 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:03:55.435 --> 00:03:57.270 position:27% line:89% align:start
[birds chirping]

00:04:01.909 --> 00:04:05.445 position:21% line:89% align:start
[lighthearted music]

00:04:56.496 --> 00:04:58.398 position:16% line:89% align:start
[Kiwa] Pretty, isn't it?

00:04:58.431 --> 00:05:01.936 position:19% line:83% align:start
The flowers bloom even
with no one to tend to them.

00:05:01.969 --> 00:05:04.906 position:27% line:83% align:start
I'm so excited to
finally live out here.

00:05:04.939 --> 00:05:08.075 position:27% line:89% align:start
[music continues]

00:05:13.848 --> 00:05:14.949 position:24% line:89% align:start
It's falling apart.

00:05:20.588 --> 00:05:23.490 position:27% line:89% align:start
[music continues]

00:05:42.442 --> 00:05:43.744 position:38% line:89% align:start
Goodness.

00:05:43.778 --> 00:05:45.980 position:13% line:83% align:start
You really outdid yourself
getting this place ready.

00:05:53.621 --> 00:05:54.454 position:38% line:89% align:start
Oh, wow.

00:05:55.156 --> 00:05:57.625 position:13% line:89% align:start
It's actually pretty nice.

00:05:57.658 --> 00:05:59.827 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Kiwa] In the old
days, this end of the house

00:05:59.861 --> 00:06:02.462 position:27% line:83% align:start
probably would've
had built-in stables.

00:06:12.874 --> 00:06:14.709 position:24% line:89% align:start
All right, you two.

00:06:14.742 --> 00:06:15.843 position:30% line:89% align:start
Come sit down.

00:06:17.778 --> 00:06:20.047 position:27% line:89% align:start
[creature howls]

00:06:22.583 --> 00:06:23.517 position:30% line:89% align:start
Is that a wolf?

00:06:23.918 --> 00:06:25.987 position:30% line:89% align:start
Never you mind.

00:06:26.020 --> 00:06:28.890 position:24% line:83% align:start
I promise there are
no wolves around here.

00:06:28.923 --> 00:06:30.591 position:7% line:89% align:start
Now, come sit with me a moment.

00:06:34.028 --> 00:06:36.197 position:33% line:83% align:start
Now, starting
today, the three of us

00:06:36.230 --> 00:06:38.165 position:7% line:89% align:start
will build new lives together.

00:06:38.199 --> 00:06:40.034 position:19% line:89% align:start
I'm very glad you came.

00:06:40.835 --> 00:06:42.069 position:27% line:89% align:start
Thanks, I guess.

00:06:51.946 --> 00:06:53.114 position:30% line:89% align:start
It's all right.

00:06:53.147 --> 00:06:55.616 position:7% line:89% align:start
Don't force yourself to speak.

00:06:55.650 --> 00:06:57.685 position:21% line:83% align:start
Just rest, and you'll
recover before you know it.

00:06:58.986 --> 00:07:02.023 position:30% line:83% align:start
To that point,
go grab your bags and relax.

00:07:02.056 --> 00:07:04.091 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'll need your help
with something in a while.

00:07:31.919 --> 00:07:33.120 position:35% line:89% align:start
[Yui sighs]

00:07:43.831 --> 00:07:45.199 position:33% line:89% align:start
My new home.

00:07:45.967 --> 00:07:47.001 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh.

00:07:50.738 --> 00:07:53.107 position:27% line:89% align:start
[rain pattering]

00:08:57.004 --> 00:09:00.007 position:30% line:89% align:start
[wood creaking]

00:09:24.265 --> 00:09:26.535 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Yui grunts]

00:09:30.404 --> 00:09:32.039 position:33% line:89% align:start
[tree thuds]

00:09:33.074 --> 00:09:34.208 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Yui] That better?

00:09:36.844 --> 00:09:38.746 position:35% line:83% align:start
You alone?
What's your name?

00:09:44.351 --> 00:09:45.252 position:27% line:89% align:start
Okay, never mind.

00:09:59.133 --> 00:10:02.269 position:30% line:89% align:start
[calming music]

00:10:26.093 --> 00:10:27.428 position:30% line:89% align:start
Hey, everyone!

00:10:27.461 --> 00:10:30.030 position:10% line:83% align:start
We have some provisions here,
courtesy of Senda Foods!

00:10:30.064 --> 00:10:31.899 position:21% line:83% align:start
Some of the packaging
is a little damaged,

00:10:31.932 --> 00:10:34.135 position:33% line:83% align:start
but the food
inside is perfectly fine.

00:10:34.802 --> 00:10:36.337 position:13% line:89% align:start
There we go. Gather round.

00:10:46.981 --> 00:10:48.282 position:27% line:89% align:start
What do you want?

00:10:48.315 --> 00:10:49.750 position:19% line:89% align:start
Apologize to that girl.

00:10:49.783 --> 00:10:51.452 position:24% line:83% align:start
Sorry, but I don't
take orders from children.

00:10:51.485 --> 00:10:52.353 position:27% line:89% align:start
[inhales sharply]

00:10:55.856 --> 00:10:56.991 position:33% line:89% align:start
There, there.

00:10:57.024 --> 00:10:57.825 position:19% line:89% align:start
You all right, darling?

00:11:00.261 --> 00:11:02.329 position:21% line:83% align:start
- Hey, what happened?
- [man grunts]

00:11:02.363 --> 00:11:05.266 position:13% line:83% align:start
Now let's get you dried off
before you catch a cold, huh?

00:11:05.299 --> 00:11:07.468 position:27% line:83% align:start
You're just about
soaked to the bone.

00:11:07.502 --> 00:11:10.771 position:21% line:83% align:start
Tanaka, will you get
a towel for this young lady?

00:11:11.172 --> 00:11:12.239 position:27% line:89% align:start
You got it!

00:11:14.308 --> 00:11:15.809 position:24% line:89% align:start
Such a sweetheart.

00:11:15.843 --> 00:11:17.444 position:13% line:89% align:start
I feel bad that she's mute.

00:11:17.478 --> 00:11:20.714 position:41% line:77% align:start
- Huh?
- More accurately,
she lost her voice.

00:11:20.748 --> 00:11:23.050 position:27% line:83% align:start
Poor thing's been
through terrible trauma.

00:11:23.083 --> 00:11:25.252 position:24% line:83% align:start
Her parents died in
a car wreck around New Year's,

00:11:25.286 --> 00:11:27.288 position:10% line:89% align:start
and she hasn't spoken since.

00:11:27.321 --> 00:11:29.056 position:24% line:89% align:start
Not a single word.

00:11:29.490 --> 00:11:32.726 position:7% line:83% align:start
She had just come to live with
some relatives in this area,

00:11:32.760 --> 00:11:36.096 position:19% line:83% align:start
but then the earthquake
hit and well, you know.

00:11:36.130 --> 00:11:38.499 position:33% line:83% align:start
She showed up
here all on her own.

00:11:38.533 --> 00:11:40.801 position:21% line:89% align:start
[inaudible dialogue]

00:11:55.182 --> 00:11:56.383 position:35% line:89% align:start
Uh, thanks.

00:11:57.184 --> 00:11:58.819 position:27% line:89% align:start
Now then, Hiyori.

00:11:58.852 --> 00:12:00.921 position:24% line:83% align:start
Are you excited to
get back to school soon?

00:12:02.957 --> 00:12:05.125 position:41% line:83% align:start
[woman]
Yoshi, could you lend me a hand?

00:12:05.159 --> 00:12:06.260 position:35% line:89% align:start
Of course!

00:12:08.996 --> 00:12:10.931 position:24% line:83% align:start
Hey, you're a high
school student, aren't you?

00:12:11.899 --> 00:12:14.068 position:7% line:83% align:start
Have you gotten to put yourself
down for registration yet?

00:12:14.101 --> 00:12:16.036 position:33% line:89% align:start
Uh, no. I...

00:12:16.370 --> 00:12:17.771 position:19% line:89% align:start
What's your name, hun?

00:12:17.805 --> 00:12:19.541 position:30% line:83% align:start
Are you staying
with family or...

00:12:19.574 --> 00:12:21.275 position:35% line:83% align:start
- I'm not.
- Where do you live?

00:12:21.942 --> 00:12:23.811 position:27% line:83% align:start
There's gotta be
somewhere you call home.

00:12:24.245 --> 00:12:26.013 position:38% line:83% align:start
You know
what? I'm actually fine.

00:12:26.548 --> 00:12:28.749 position:41% line:83% align:start
- Wait.
- Oh, she's with me.

00:12:29.049 --> 00:12:30.117 position:27% line:89% align:start
I'm her grandma.

00:12:30.985 --> 00:12:32.119 position:30% line:89% align:start
Her name is...

00:12:33.153 --> 00:12:37.391 position:24% line:83% align:start
Oh, it's not Akemi,
and I know it's not Sanae,

00:12:37.424 --> 00:12:39.893 position:7% line:89% align:start
it's one of those trendy names.

00:12:40.928 --> 00:12:42.930 position:27% line:83% align:start
- [Yui] Yui.
- Ah, there we go.

00:12:42.963 --> 00:12:44.398 position:27% line:89% align:start
Yui, I knew that.

00:12:45.199 --> 00:12:46.800 position:21% line:89% align:start
And this little one.

00:12:46.834 --> 00:12:48.202 position:24% line:89% align:start
Really? Hiyori too?

00:12:48.235 --> 00:12:50.137 position:16% line:89% align:start
That's right, Hiyori too.

00:12:50.838 --> 00:12:52.373 position:21% line:83% align:start
[woman] You're really
her grandmother, ma'am?

00:12:52.940 --> 00:12:54.141 position:30% line:89% align:start
Of course I am.

00:12:54.174 --> 00:12:56.076 position:30% line:83% align:start
Why else would
I have come to pick her up?

00:12:57.111 --> 00:13:00.047 position:16% line:83% align:start
You've had to go through
so much at such a young age,

00:13:00.080 --> 00:13:02.082 position:7% line:89% align:start
but you've never once given up.

00:13:02.116 --> 00:13:03.250 position:19% line:89% align:start
I'm very proud of you.

00:13:03.284 --> 00:13:05.986 position:30% line:89% align:start
[gentle music]

00:13:07.454 --> 00:13:09.056 position:19% line:89% align:start
They are my grandkids,

00:13:09.089 --> 00:13:11.125 position:5% line:89% align:start
but it's our first time meeting.

00:13:11.158 --> 00:13:13.561 position:30% line:83% align:start
And my memory's
foggy these days,

00:13:13.595 --> 00:13:16.063 position:30% line:83% align:start
so it can take
a while for names to sink in.

00:13:16.864 --> 00:13:20.134 position:16% line:83% align:start
Now, shall we get going?
Get your things.

00:13:20.167 --> 00:13:23.003 position:30% line:83% align:start
Sorry, but may
I ask your name first?

00:13:23.037 --> 00:13:25.607 position:24% line:83% align:start
- I'm Kiwa Yamana.
- [woman] And you live...

00:13:25.640 --> 00:13:29.276 position:16% line:83% align:start
There's a place ready and
waiting for us in Kitsunezaki.

00:13:29.310 --> 00:13:30.878 position:7% line:89% align:start
We'll discuss the details soon,

00:13:31.979 --> 00:13:34.448 position:27% line:83% align:start
but I think it's
going to be wonderful.

00:13:39.587 --> 00:13:42.524 position:13% line:83% align:start
If you girls are all alone,
know you have a place with me.

00:13:45.459 --> 00:13:47.161 position:13% line:89% align:start
Never you mind, all right?

00:13:48.329 --> 00:13:50.464 position:5% line:89% align:start
It just means don't worry, dear.

00:13:51.131 --> 00:13:52.833 position:35% line:83% align:start
Looks like
it stopped raining too.

00:14:03.043 --> 00:14:04.612 position:27% line:83% align:start
I was just going
with the flow before,

00:14:04.646 --> 00:14:06.313 position:7% line:89% align:start
but can we trust this old lady?

00:14:10.552 --> 00:14:12.286 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Kiwa] Yui, Hiyori.

00:14:14.388 --> 00:14:17.592 position:13% line:83% align:start
Could I trouble you ladies
to follow me for just a moment?

00:14:19.661 --> 00:14:21.028 position:30% line:89% align:start
[metal clangs]

00:14:21.061 --> 00:14:22.129 position:30% line:89% align:start
Why? What for?

00:14:24.198 --> 00:14:25.399 position:27% line:83% align:start
At least tell us
where we're going.

00:14:32.640 --> 00:14:34.875 position:35% line:89% align:start
Ugh! Here.

00:14:35.075 --> 00:14:37.277 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Kiwa] For today,
just cut up to the well,

00:14:37.311 --> 00:14:39.313 position:7% line:89% align:start
then go clean the halls, okay?

00:14:39.681 --> 00:14:41.014 position:38% line:89% align:start
The well?

00:14:41.048 --> 00:14:43.618 position:30% line:89% align:start
[mellow music]

00:14:45.185 --> 00:14:46.186 position:38% line:89% align:start
Come on!

00:14:48.590 --> 00:14:51.058 position:27% line:89% align:start
[water splashes]

00:14:59.233 --> 00:15:01.402 position:27% line:89% align:start
[music continues]

00:15:08.543 --> 00:15:10.978 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Yui grunts]

00:15:15.449 --> 00:15:18.285 position:19% line:89% align:start
[Yui breathes heavily]

00:15:22.256 --> 00:15:25.426 position:27% line:89% align:start
[music continues]

00:15:31.398 --> 00:15:34.602 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Yui grunts]

00:15:50.350 --> 00:15:51.653 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Yui groans]

00:15:51.686 --> 00:15:53.555 position:44% line:89% align:start
Jeez!

00:15:53.588 --> 00:15:55.657 position:13% line:83% align:start
Is this why she brought us
all the way out here? To clean?

00:15:57.592 --> 00:15:58.626 position:30% line:89% align:start
[paper squeaks]

00:15:59.193 --> 00:16:00.027 position:44% line:89% align:start
Um...

00:16:03.397 --> 00:16:06.467 position:10% line:83% align:start
Do sliding doors usually make
that sound when they get torn?

00:16:07.669 --> 00:16:09.537 position:33% line:83% align:start
[Kiwa] Sounds
like you're all done.

00:16:09.571 --> 00:16:11.271 position:33% line:83% align:start
Come see what
we're having for dinner.

00:16:28.489 --> 00:16:31.458 position:27% line:89% align:start
[steam whistles]

00:16:36.363 --> 00:16:38.332 position:7% line:89% align:start
[Kiwa] This is urui miso soup.

00:16:38.365 --> 00:16:39.534 position:44% line:89% align:start
Urui?

00:16:39.567 --> 00:16:41.201 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Kiwa] It all came
out of the lawn clippings

00:16:41.235 --> 00:16:42.604 position:21% line:89% align:start
you two cut earlier.

00:16:42.637 --> 00:16:46.039 position:7% line:83% align:start
We'll also have mugwort tempura
and some wild rocambole.

00:16:46.473 --> 00:16:47.642 position:24% line:89% align:start
So it's all grass?

00:16:47.675 --> 00:16:49.544 position:19% line:89% align:start
Well, hold your horses.

00:16:50.244 --> 00:16:53.013 position:33% line:83% align:start
For our main
course, hamburger steaks.

00:17:02.322 --> 00:17:04.559 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Yui sniffs]

00:17:06.159 --> 00:17:07.427 position:33% line:89% align:start
Smells good.

00:17:07.695 --> 00:17:09.363 position:10% line:89% align:start
Then what are we waiting for?

00:17:10.832 --> 00:17:12.199 position:21% line:89% align:start
[Yui] Uh, thank you.

00:17:31.786 --> 00:17:32.820 position:33% line:89% align:start
Pretty good.

00:17:34.254 --> 00:17:36.591 position:21% line:89% align:start
[lighthearted music]

00:17:42.262 --> 00:17:44.732 position:24% line:83% align:start
Don't forget to try
some of the tempura too.

00:17:50.470 --> 00:17:51.305 position:33% line:89% align:start
Really good.

00:17:54.207 --> 00:17:57.277 position:27% line:89% align:start
[music continues]

00:18:18.933 --> 00:18:21.268 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Kiwa] And we have
milk pudding for dessert.

00:18:22.402 --> 00:18:23.705 position:7% line:89% align:start
[Yui] This has grass in it too?

00:18:28.475 --> 00:18:29.510 position:38% line:89% align:start
Oh, wow.

00:18:38.620 --> 00:18:40.320 position:13% line:89% align:start
[Yui] Oh, thank you again.

00:18:41.254 --> 00:18:42.255 position:24% line:89% align:start
Oh, it was nothing.

00:18:43.825 --> 00:18:45.492 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Yui] I never had
food like this at home.

00:18:48.295 --> 00:18:49.897 position:35% line:89% align:start
[Yui gasps]

00:18:52.634 --> 00:18:53.935 position:38% line:83% align:start
Why don't
you put your things away

00:18:53.968 --> 00:18:56.303 position:7% line:89% align:start
and hop in the bath before bed?

00:18:56.336 --> 00:18:57.872 position:5% line:89% align:start
Do you need a change of clothes?

00:18:57.905 --> 00:18:59.574 position:24% line:89% align:start
No, I have plenty.

00:18:59.607 --> 00:19:00.942 position:16% line:89% align:start
That's good, but I'm sure

00:19:00.975 --> 00:19:02.710 position:30% line:83% align:start
you're missing
other things, right?

00:19:02.744 --> 00:19:05.813 position:13% line:83% align:start
So make a list, and we can
all go to Masuda Mall tomorrow.

00:19:15.723 --> 00:19:17.759 position:16% line:83% align:start
Don't let your guard down
just because the food was good.

00:19:17.792 --> 00:19:19.426 position:24% line:89% align:start
All right, Hiyori?

00:19:19.459 --> 00:19:20.862 position:27% line:89% align:start
There's a story.

00:19:20.895 --> 00:19:21.929 position:33% line:89% align:start
How's it go?

00:19:30.505 --> 00:19:32.607 position:10% line:89% align:start
"Kids get lured in with food

00:19:32.640 --> 00:19:35.510 position:27% line:83% align:start
so a stranger can
fatten them up like livestock."

00:19:35.543 --> 00:19:36.744 position:27% line:83% align:start
- [wind blowing]
- Uh-uh.

00:19:36.778 --> 00:19:38.846 position:30% line:89% align:start
[eerie moaning]

00:19:39.479 --> 00:19:41.415 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Kiwa] Are you two
about ready for your bath?

00:19:45.019 --> 00:19:48.188 position:30% line:89% align:start
[fire crackles]

00:19:49.356 --> 00:19:51.258 position:27% line:89% align:start
[water splashes]

00:19:52.694 --> 00:19:54.428 position:19% line:89% align:start
That story I mentioned.

00:19:54.862 --> 00:19:57.497 position:33% line:83% align:start
If I remember
correctly, an evil witch

00:19:57.532 --> 00:19:59.734 position:19% line:83% align:start
invites these abandoned
siblings into her home.

00:19:59.767 --> 00:20:02.637 position:10% line:83% align:start
She feeds them, then prepares
a big pot of boiling water

00:20:02.670 --> 00:20:03.705 position:33% line:89% align:start
to cook them.

00:20:04.739 --> 00:20:05.707 position:30% line:89% align:start
Sound familiar?

00:20:11.846 --> 00:20:13.246 position:13% line:89% align:start
You girls have a nice bath?

00:20:14.982 --> 00:20:15.983 position:38% line:89% align:start
I guess.

00:20:16.784 --> 00:20:17.985 position:16% line:89% align:start
What's the matter, dear?

00:20:19.020 --> 00:20:20.353 position:35% line:89% align:start
This house.

00:20:20.387 --> 00:20:21.254 position:33% line:89% align:start
Why is it...

00:20:22.523 --> 00:20:24.424 position:24% line:89% align:start
you know, out here?

00:20:24.826 --> 00:20:25.893 position:16% line:89% align:start
I mean, look, we don't--

00:20:26.326 --> 00:20:29.429 position:16% line:89% align:start
[Kiwa] I know. Come, sit.

